fields.name: Addr
fields.description: The IP or hostname and possibly port of the client connection that initiated the event. This is the RemoteAddr from the standard http request.

fields.name: Host
fields.description: The externally accessible hostname of the registry instance, as specified by the http host header on incoming requests.

fields.name: Id
fields.description: The ID of the request that initiated the event.

fields.name: Method
fields.description: The request method that generated the event.

fields.name: Useragent
fields.description: The user agent header of the request.
